{"tid":2251454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尼日尼亞黒警射殺示威者","createTime":"2020-10-20T22:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T01:41:10.000Z","uid":160980,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"483f3fc95088dd68046fad5df6eef0b8647ac4d0","tid":2251454,"uid":160980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:21:47.000Z","msg":"尼日尼亞手足也有五大訴求，也被黑警射殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNigerian security forces opened fire on protesters in Lagos in an escalation of violence before a lockdown was imposed on Africa&rsquo;s most-populous city to quell growing rallies against police brutality in the OPEC nation.<br />\n<br />\nA Nigerian Red Cross Society official said at least two civilians were shot dead in the incident, adding to at least six other deaths in the country on Tuesday. The Lagos state government said it&rsquo;s ordered an investigation into the incident.<br />\n<br />\nSpokespeople for the Nigerian police and army didn&rsquo;t immediately answer calls by Bloomberg seeking comment.<br />\n<br />\nThe shooting came hours after the governor of Lagos state announced a 24-hour curfew to try and end disruptions in a region that&rsquo;s home to more than 22 million people and houses the headquarters of Nigeria&rsquo;s biggest banks. Before today, the protests have been largely peaceful, with the government issuing a directive to its security forces not to use <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-10-20/losses-mount-from-nigerian-protests-against-police-brutality?srnd=premium-africa&amp;sref=d39KtWbu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-10-20%2Flosses-mount-from-nigerian-protests-against-police-brutality%3Fsrnd%3Dpremium-africa%26sref%3Dd39KtWbu&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=3b6de415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-10-20/losses-mount-from-nigerian-protests-against-police-brutality?srnd=premium-africa&amp;sref=d39KtWbu</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i2-wp-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/SARS-2.jpg?w=828&amp;ssl=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-wp-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.vanguardngr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FSARS-2.jpg%3Fw%3D828%26ssl%3D1&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=b0053211\" target=\"_blank\">https://i2-wp-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/SARS-2.jpg?w=828&amp;ssl=1</a>"},{"pid":"1a59a550a3b8b2e9d861a588b3158588375c7a7f","tid":2251454,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:23:01.000Z","msg":"twitter #EndSARS<br />\nspread the words"},{"pid":"480028eb523d5c77e8c19da089293f15d6e0ade9","tid":2251454,"uid":270889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ndidi25/status/1318676254623698947?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNdidi25%2Fstatus%2F1318676254623698947%3Fs%3D20&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=cebac365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNdidi25%2Fstatus%2F1318676254623698947%3Fs%3D20&h=70018c9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ndidi25/status/1318676254623698947?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"561d956cf34caeb30e966fe429f9126a9714819b","tid":2251454,"uid":270889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:24:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rioferdy5/status/1318676050528841731?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frioferdy5%2Fstatus%2F1318676050528841731%3Fs%3D20&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=33fe2a29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u